{"tid":533793,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 李嘉欣紅唇Look撐愛駒","createTime":"2018-01-19T07:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T16:14:24.000Z","uid":48905,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"86a037801dddc27ed304d9f4fc9f1045fc800095","tid":533793,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:15:16.000Z","msg":"「大美人」李嘉欣與老公許晉亨（亨亨）現身馬場，兩人拖住手大晒恩愛，真係令人葡萄！亨亨以深色西裝Look現身，而嘉欣就化上搶眼嘅紅唇妝，以白恤衫、黑裙、黑外套再襯鮮紅色長靴示人，認真Sharp醒！據知今晚許家嘅愛駒「估惑」會再出場，上次同系「獻惑」幫許世勳先生贏夠100場，但嘉欣就冇到場，唔通今晚嚟補拉頭馬？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，剛剛開完紅館處女個唱嘅王灝兒（JW），今晚都有同男友葉韋彤嚟到馬場，不過佢哋匹愛駒「首驫」唔知係咪知道主人嚟捧場太High，竟然未開閘就衝咗出嚟，結果要重新入多次閘出賽，最終只係跑尾二。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/151507_e9abf0d58c5f9dc6cd7d9a9f113eb6b5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F151507_e9abf0d58c5f9dc6cd7d9a9f113eb6b5.png&h=7463f87d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad33ebd29ac7f429c27ffecbf55d3046a3dc3abf","tid":533793,"uid":42820,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:17:14.000Z","msg":"水鞋？"},{"pid":"1f39cbf2720a014211ef56ea7a3c0cfda5b4a643","tid":533793,"uid":137764,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:22:50.000Z","msg":"對鞋柒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3cf77b65cda70b10c57ab333c5671fafd04c7e","tid":533793,"uid":22218,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:24:49.000Z","msg":"唔拉頭馬養隻馬嚟把撚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a63b167220fa25c8c12764aa0dd1f297a7eff3","tid":533793,"uid":15,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:25:28.000Z","msg":"唉, 廢事嘈呀"},{"pid":"6a5ca68dbdcded88c5c661157d5f1a51fb889ba3","tid":533793,"uid":30510,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:25:42.0